CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Alpine Immune Sciences Inc is a clinical-stage biopharmaceutical company. It is engaged in discovering and developing innovative, protein-based immunotherapies to treat cancer and autoimmune and inflammatory diseases. The company's proprietary scientific platform uses a process known as directed evolution to create therapeutics capable of modulating human immune system proteins. Its product pipeline includes ALPN-101 and ALPN-202.
